name: Where the Hell is My Package!!
name_original: Where the Hell is My Package!!
description:
Greg recently bought something on the internet and have been very excited about it. The delivery hasn't arrived since then. Furious, he decided to personally go to the delivery depot and make the delivery arrive at his house as soon as possible. To do this, he needs to look for the package that contains his delivery, place the invoice on it and make it depart in one of the delivery trucks.
